highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 874 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #9.
“Crazy Train” by Ozzy Osbourne is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #79.
“Mama, I'm Coming Home” by Ozzy Osbourne is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 114 spots at #76.
